      <h2>ingredients</h2>
        
        <ul class="ingredients"><li class="ingredient" itemprop="ingredients">1 750-ml bottle dry white wine</li><li class="ingredient" itemprop="ingredients">1 1/2 cups Essensia (orange Muscat, a sweet dessert wine)</li><li class="ingredient" itemprop="ingredients">1 1/2 cups sliced strawberries</li><li class="ingredient" itemprop="ingredients">1 cup peach liqueur</li><li class="ingredient" itemprop="ingredients">3 peaches, each cut into 12 slices</li><li class="ingredient" itemprop="ingredients">1 large orange, cut crosswise into 6 slices</li><li class="ingredient" itemprop="ingredients">1 large lemon, cut crosswise into 6 slices</li><li class="ingredient" itemprop="ingredients">1/4 cup strawberry syrup (optional)</li><li class="ingredient" itemprop="ingredients">3 to 4 cups ice cubes</li></ul>
 </div>
